Comment: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:00.12,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:120120,120120}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:04.91,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121204,124916}Maya's rival, Ayumi, has increased\Nher reputation even further…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:124916,127711}…with her acting in "The Prince and the Pauper."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:11.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:127711,131840}So has Maya, who gained the public's attention\Nplaying a small baby sitter role at Eishin Za.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:15.46,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:131840,135469}However, Harada Kikuko\Nof Eishin Za fears her talent…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:20.18,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:135469,140182}…calling it a stage storm, that separates\NMaya from the other actors on the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:27.18,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141141,147189}{\an5\pos(192,200)\fscy95\blur1\fad(500,0)}—Episode 12—\NI'm Catherine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.27,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:152319,154279}"The Prince and the Pauper"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152819,156490}One of my friends in college\Nis putting a small acting group together…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156490,162495}…and is looking for some people\Nto work backstage with equipment and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162495,163162}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.16,0:02:44.66,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:163162,164665}Free People
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165248,169878}We have a children's play at a kindergarten\Nand we would like you to come…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169878,172964}…but I wonder if it will be okay,\Nsince you are still in junior high…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172964,175926}Yes!\NI'll do the best I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.26,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:181807,184267}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.64,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188647,192651}{\i1}Maya… I wonder what she's up to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192651,196029}{\i1}Having a crazy dream\Nto become an actress and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196029,198823}{\i1}I hope she's not hurt and crying and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213088,215966}{\i1}Blood! Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.72,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219720,223473}About the Metropolitan Town Building,\Nwhich will open next October…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223473,228311}…the decisions regarding tenants, including several\Nboutiques and restaurants, have all been made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228311,233275}What about the opening play for\Nthe Metropolitan Theater on the 10th floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.27,0:03:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233275,239030}Yes, we have decided on the play\N"The Miracle Worker," about Helen Keller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239030,243452}Hmm. "The Miracle Worker,"\Nabout the blind girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243452,250083}We're planning to audition for the role of Helen,\Nbut the best candidate so far is Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:250083,251376}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251376,255422}She has gotten much better\Nsince "The Prince and the Pauper."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255422,258382}But, she does have one rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258382,259259}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.92,0:04:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261928,264723}Mr. Masumi, the next meeting is about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264723,265557}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265557,268935}Mr. Masumi, who is this rival\Nof Himekawa Ayumi's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269770,272898}You have a lot of time until next summer…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272898,276234}…so do some research and get\Nas many good candidates for Helen as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277694,281031}{\i1}I wonder who Himekawa Ayumi's rival is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.15,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:279738,282157}Fukune Kindergarten
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290623,292125}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292584,295086}Oh, no, there has been an accident on the road?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296379,298256}Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298256,302761}The members will be a little late due to traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302761,305180}Oh, that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306014,309518}We can't have these kids waiting any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309851,312729}Hey, everyone, be quiet, quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.27,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314272,318985}The people from the acting group\Nwill be a little late, so let's hear some stories first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320111,325617}A long, long time ago,\Nthere was a fair skinned, beautiful princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.61,0:05:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325617,330038}People called her Snow White.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.58,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330580,332833}This is not working…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336962,340090}You're a big boy, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.09,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340090,342717}But it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.71,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342717,345470}Good boy, but don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345470,349099}Okay, I'll tell you the rest of the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349099,355647}Snow White's mother, the queen,\Nwas really a scary witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.89,0:06:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356898,360235}Everyday she would stand up\Nin front of a big mirror, and say:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360235,364406}"Mirror, mirror on the wall…"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364406,370579}"Who is the fairest of them all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370579,371955}Then the mirror would say:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371955,376918}"The most beautiful woman\Nin the world is you, my Queen."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382507,385760}But one day, she asked the same question,\Nand the mirror answered:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.76,0:06:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385760,391016}"The most beautiful woman\Nin the world is Snow White."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395854,397313}O-Oh, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398690,399816}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399816,403820}Why don't you continue playing\Ntill the members get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403820,405864}In fact, on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406239,409743}Yeah, please!\NDo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413204,415164}But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416708,418627}Long time no see, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418627,421212}I know, it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422714,425383}That girl is scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425383,426592}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426592,429054}The play she played on was stormed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430513,434559}All the audience was looking at her,\Neven though she only had a small role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434559,441107}Anyone who stands on the stage with her\Nis in her way, and becomes a shadow of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442525,445528}So, I decided that I shouldn't use her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.52,0:07:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445528,450283}I don't want Eishin Za to be\Nmessed up because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:450283,453995}Her talent can be a threat to other actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453995,457707}While she's young, I bet she will be envied…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457707,462295}…and get kicked out of many theaters\Nbecause of her talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462295,467050}But, Miss Harada, she will get\Nher recognition someday—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467050,469803}Because people want to see her more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470836,472263}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472263,477560}There will be a day\Nwhen she will be supported by the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.56,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477560,479104}It will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486319,488238}We're so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488238,490532}Yeah, I bet the kids must be out of control.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490532,492909}Oh, you'll give me that red apple?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492909,496788}I'm sorry, but I'm not supposed\Nto eat anything from strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496788,498789}"But, young lady…"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498789,500582}Oh! The members are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500582,503503}Oh, I'm sorry!\NI didn't notice you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503503,506214}Oh no, I apologize for being late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506214,511636}Okay, everyone, the members are here,\Nso big sister's story is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511636,515347}No, I want to hear her!\NHer story!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520562,522814}She has so much talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525608,533450}I'm really sorry, but since the kids are like this,\Nwould you mind waiting till Snow White is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533450,534284}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534284,535660}I'm sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535660,536411}Hey…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536411,538079}What can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.07,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538079,540665}The kids want to see her play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542459,547589}Okay, everyone.\NBig sister will finish Snow White.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555388,557182}{\i1}She took our stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560477,562020}Then, we're all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562020,563521}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567150,571613}{\i1}It seems like she was just telling a story,\Nbut it was definitely a one-person play.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574282,578870}{\i1}It's not sophisticated, but she had something\Nthat grabbed everyone's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578870,581372}{\i1}That's the real attraction of actors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:46.87,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:581872,586877}{\fad(3000,0)}Shirayuri College
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587796,590507}Here are your earnings for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:590507,591800}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591800,594385}Also, you don't have to come anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.38,0:09:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594385,595970}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595970,596887}W-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596887,600809}You've hurt our pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609067,611236}{\i1}They're just envious, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611236,614197}{\i1}You were kicked out because of your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615365,617700}Just forget about it, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617700,621371}Let's think about something that you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621371,624415}– Something that I like…\N– You like acting, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624415,625458}Rei…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625458,628627}No matter what happens, you have acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628627,632882}As long as you don't throw that away,\Nacting won't throw you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632882,633633}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633633,635009}Acting. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635009,638888}No matter what happens,\NI have acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638888,640181}No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640181,641933}{\i1}What a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641933,645728}{\i1}She was so depressed just a minute ago,\Nbut she cheers up just by thinking about acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:648231,649314}Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655113,656156}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.61,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657615,661035}The young Catherine from "Wuthering Heights?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661035,661744}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661744,666124}The president of Tōyō Theater\Nsaw you acting for Eishin Za before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666124,669836}He would like you to come\Nand audition for Catherine's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669836,672755}Wow, Maya!\NThat's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672755,674424}Catherine's role!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674424,676968}It's when she's young,\Nbut that's a main role!
Comment: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:20.72,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:680722,680722}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:24.51,0:11:24.51,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:684516,684516}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:27.47,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:687478,687478}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693276,696571}Please wait in the waiting room\Ntill the audition starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696571,698781}The other two are already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698781,699490}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:49.33,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:705163,709334}Wuthering Heights
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705788,707832}Here's the script for the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707832,710919}Read it thoroughly and memorize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710919,711628}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736110,738363}{\i1}I wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738363,742825}Everyone, please meet Majima Ryo,\Nwho will play the young Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743660,745453}Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745453,747497}{\i1}The young Heathcliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754504,755797}Let me introduce everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755797,759968}Mr. Murase, the chief director\Nfor "Wuthering Heights."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759968,762762}Mr. Sawaki, the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762762,765515}Mr. Suzumura, the producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765515,768017}Ms. Natsu Eriko,\Nwho will play Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768017,771229}…and Mr. Hideaki Kagawa,\Nwho will play Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771229,773147}Now, we'll begin the audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773147,775733}Please state your name\Nand age, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775733,778194}Tanaka Keiko, 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778194,780613}Egawa Yuki, 16.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780613,783199}Kitajima Maya, 15.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783199,789789}Ms. Egawa, you're from the same theater as\NMajima Ryo, who'll play the young Heathcliff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789789,790665}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793251,796879}Ms. Egawa, have you ever read\N"Wuthering Heights?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.87,0:13:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796879,798715}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.71,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798715,799841}What about you, Ms. Tanaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799841,801592}Yes, I've read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801592,802927}Ms. Kitajima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802927,805096}No, I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805096,808850}Hmm. Ms. Tanaka, what do you think\Nabout the heroine, Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.01,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809017,810351}{\i1}Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810601,814605}I think she's passionate and a great woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814605,817483}I see.\NWhat about you, Ms. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817483,821863}I love her passionate love towards Heathcliff…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821863,824115}{\i1}I should have read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:48.61,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:824365,828619}Maya had to take the audition without knowing\Nthe story of "Wuthering Heights"…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.08,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:828619,831080}…nor the role of Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831748,835626}Okay, please come out as Catherine, Ms. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835626,836461}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840256,841090}Ms. Tanaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841090,841674}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843301,848055}{\i1}What should I do?\NI don't know how Catherine walks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848848,850141}Ms. Kitajima.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850725,851934}Ms. Kitajima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862111,867033}I'm sorry, I haven't read\N"Wuthering Heights…"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867033,870912}…so I don't know\Nhow to walk as Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.91,0:14:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870912,871954}I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:38.71,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:873581,878711}It was beyond description how the audition went\Nfor Maya not knowing Catherine's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880004,883841}{\i1}Oh, no, I couldn't wear the mask of Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:885676,887485}I really want to get this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.48,0:14:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:887485,890431}I want to be on stage with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.43,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890431,891682}You will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891682,893726}You were the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893726,896294}You are the only one to be my lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896294,898189}Even on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898189,899232}Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899941,902652}So, Egawa Yuki, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902652,905947}Yes, she had the atmosphere\Nand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905947,910535}Anyhow, what's up\Nwith the girl, Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910535,914122}She just could not give 100% of her talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:914122,915540}Mr. President!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:915540,919377}Since she didn't understand\Nwho Catherine really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919377,925133}But, it will be easier to train her rather than\Nthe others who already have presumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932974,935977}We'll announce Catherine's role.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:938729,940940}{\i1}It wouldn't be me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941315,942442}Ms. Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946654,948197}Kitajima Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948197,949740}M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949740,951451}Re-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953244,956998}Yes.\NYou'll play Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956998,958374}{\i1}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.04,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963045,964922}Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:964922,965673}Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965673,967341}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967675,969801}Well, learn from everyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969801,974765}Excuse me, but can you tell me why,\Nwhy she was chosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977935,981063}In one word – possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.06,0:16:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981063,982648}Possibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982648,983983}{\i1}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986918,989488}{\i1}This girl will play Catherine?\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.48,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989488,992407}It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993493,994911}Y-You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995703,999165}{\i1}Ryo, I wanted to be\Nyour lover on stage, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002043,1006714}You must understand, this is a big bet\Nfor us to give you the role, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006714,1008591}You have to do the best\Nyou can, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1008591,1009925}Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.51,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011511,1014347}{\i1}Catherine. I'm Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014347,1015264}{\i1}Catherine…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1021812,1023856}Congratulations, Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027485,1028694}She's been like this all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028694,1030947}She hasn't even noticed that we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032990,1036244}{\i1}What can I do\Nto become Catherine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040414,1046003}To understand people, you have to understand\Nthe circumstances in which they were brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047255,1049966}Then, you will start understanding little by little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.92,0:17:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050925,1052134}{\i1}Circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057640,1059058}{\i1}Circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060893,1064397}{\i1}The circumstances she grew up with.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.31,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066315,1070653}Heathcliff, why did you come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070653,1072822}No, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072822,1074824}To destroy everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074824,1076534}Natsu, great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076534,1078911}It's only a script reading,\Nbut look at her powerful acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1079579,1080913}Heathcliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080913,1086002}Wow, a Catherine that's\Npassionate, selfish and wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.16,0:18:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087169,1089714}I'm not understanding Catherine yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092800,1098556}The most painful punishment for Catherine\Nis not being able to play with Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098556,1100683}But what about Heathcliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100683,1104312}Not to be with Catherine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104312,1108065}The most painful punishment for Catherine\Nis not being able to be with Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119702,1121746}That's Kazuo.\NHe's looking at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1121746,1124248}Oh, no!\NHe's so hardheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124248,1126292}And he smells, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129712,1132632}You go play by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1136886,1138596}Ouch! Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138596,1140556}We'll never play with you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146604,1148022}Oh, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150066,1152443}Oh, no!\NYou're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.78,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160785,1162119}No one's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163287,1165164}Mom and Dad are both at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169627,1170878}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.29,0:19:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172296,1174090}Shiny cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174757,1177176}My dad bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177176,1178427}Can I play with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178427,1180763}Yeah. Let's race each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180763,1182014}I'll be the police car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182014,1185976}Okay.\NReady, get set, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190314,1194276}{\i1}Wow, I wonder how many years it has been\Nsince we've been able to play with toys like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194276,1196195}{\i1}Play?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.19,0:20:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196195,1200783}{\i1}I wonder if Heathcliff and Catherine played?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200783,1204745}{\i1}They didn't have any other friends…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204745,1207498}{\i1}…nor all these toys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214380,1215131}Kazuo!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215131,1217675}Oh, Mom!\NWelcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219427,1221470}Oh, hi, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221470,1224014}W-Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.01,0:20:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224014,1227935}This girl here,\Nshe helped me when I fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227935,1230271}Here, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.68,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230688,1236235}Oh, thank you very much,\Nand to play with Kazuo as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236235,1238195}My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1239739,1243534}Hey, let's play with this again!\NHere, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243534,1245035}Here, Kazuo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.03,0:20:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245035,1248998}…big sister has to go home soon.\NIt's getting late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.58,0:20:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250583,1252460}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.79,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256797,1257673}Kazuo…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259925,1261218}Kazuo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261218,1263262}No, don't go yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263262,1264680}Stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264680,1267558}No, don't go, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268434,1269769}{\i1}Kazuo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269769,1271227}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.22,0:21:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271227,1274231}In the daytime,\Nhe's usually by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274231,1276692}So he must be really happy\Nthat you played with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276692,1281405}No, don't go, sister.\NSister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284658,1287745}{\i1}Kazuo, he's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288662,1292249}{\i1}But poor Kazuo,\Nhe's always all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292500,1294460}{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294919,1296420}{\i1}All alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1296670,1302343}{\i1}To understand people you have to understand\Nthe circumstances in which they were brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303093,1304595}{\i1}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305888,1309850}{\i1}She lives in the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309850,1314438}{\i1}There was no one to play with,\Nand she was all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.43,0:21:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314438,1317691}{\i1}The only person to play with\Nwas Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:22:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317691,1322738}{\i1}They didn't have any toys,\Nbut all they had was each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322738,1327576}{\i1}Heathcliff for Catherine,\Nand Catherine for Heathcliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.58,0:22:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335584,1340589}{\i1}She's honest to her true feelings,\Nand so she's wild and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.71,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340714,1342007}{\i1}No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1345553,1347429}{\i1}I can…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1347429,1349932}{\i1}I can become Catherine!
Comment: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:50.95,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370953,1370953}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.33,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1378200,1384330}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:10.42,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384330,1390420}{\blur3}…and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.42,0:23:22.43,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1390420,1402430}{\blur3}Somewhere calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.43,0:23:34.57,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1402430,1414570}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:40.45,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414570,1420450}{\blur3}…more surer than words…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.45,0:23:46.58,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1420450,1426580}{\blur3}…telling us gently…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:52.67,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426580,1432670}{\blur3}…that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:58.76,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432670,1438760}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:04.77,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1438760,1444770}{\blur3}…for the dream\Non my cheek…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.77,0:24:10.73,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1444770,1450730}{\blur3\fad(0,500)}…belongs to you.
